                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990508-41-off239 t17990508-41-cd238"></join>, was possessed of a Bil of Exchange, for the payment of money, to the tenor following:Â£.28 16s. Devonshire Bank.</p>
               <p>Thirty days after date, pay to the order of Mr. 
               <persName id="t17990508-41-person534">
                  Thomas
                   Scott
               <interp inst="t17990508-41-person534" type="surname" value="Scott"></interp>
