            , London.</p>
               <p>And <rs id="t17990508-41-off239" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17990508-41-off239" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990508-41-off239" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               upon which Bill of Exchange were certain endorsements, as follow: 
                     <persName id="t17990508-41-person538">
                        Thomas
                         Scott
                     <interp inst="t17990508-41-person538" type="surname" value="Scott"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-person538" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-person538" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , R. Dudley; and being so possessed of the said bill, feloniously did utter as true, a false, forged, and <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179905080063"></xptr>counterfeited endorsement upon the said bill, purporting to be an assignment of the said bill under the hand of 
                     <persName id="t17990508-41-person539">
                        Samuel
                         Taylor
                     <interp inst="t17990508-41-person539" type="surname" value="Taylor"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-person539" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-person539" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , which said forged endorsement is as follows: "
                     <persName id="t17990508-41-person540">
                        Samuel
                         Taylor
                     <interp inst="t17990508-41-person540" type="surname" value="Taylor"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-person540" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-person540" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  ;" with intent to defraud 
                     <persName id="t17990508-41-victim541" type="victimName">Messrs. Daubeny, and <rs id="t17990508-41-viclabel240" type="occupation">Company</rs>
                        <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990508-41-victim541 t17990508-41-viclabel240"></join>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-victim541" type="surname" value="Daubeny"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-victim541" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , of Bristol
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Count. Charging it to be with intent to defraud 
               
                  <persName id="t17990508-41-victim543" type="victimName">
