            .</p>
               <p>Third Count. Charging it to be with intent to defraud 
               <persName id="t17990508-41-victim544" type="victimName">
                  Francis and 
                        
                           <persName id="t17990508-41-victim546" type="victimName">
                              William 
                              Gosling
                           <interp inst="t17990508-41-victim546" type="surname" value="Gosling"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-victim546" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17990508-41-victim546" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                        
                     
                     <interp inst="t17990508-41-victim544" type="surname" value="Gosling"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990508-41-victim544" type="given" value="Francis"></interp>
